  description="Learn how we collect, use, and protect your information when you use our service."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-y-10 py-8 md:py-12">
    <Container className="max-w-3xl">
      <div class="prose">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

        <p>
          Your privacy is important to us. This Privacy Policy explains how we
          collect, use, and protect your information when you use our service.
        </p>

        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>
          We may collect limited personal and usage information to operate and
          improve the service.
        </p>

        <h3>Analytics</h3>
        <p>
          We use privacy-focused analytics tools to understand how the service
          is used:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Umami</strong> â€“ for website traffic analytics</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          These tools may collect anonymized or pseudonymized usage data such as
          page views, device information, and interaction events.
        </p>

        <h3>AI Services</h3>
        <p>We use third-party AI services to provide certain features:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>OpenAI</strong></li>
